data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home sits on 3.58+/- open and level acres, offering beautiful country views in every direction. Inside, you'll find an inviting living space open to the kitchen and dining area. The heart of this home is the kitchen, complete with an island and an abundance of cabinet space. The 30' x 40' shop is a handyman's paradise, featuring built-in workbench and cabinets for all your DIY projects. The home has had several updates in the last two years including a new septic tank, well pump, vinyl energy efficient windows, vinyl sliding glass door, and a water filtration/ reverse osmosis system. There are apple and pear trees in the yard as well as the cutest playhouse. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your forever home. Schedule a showing today and start living the tranquil country lifestyle you've always dreamed of!
